      • RProperty

        public RProperty(java.lang.String n,
                 int p,
                 int c,
                 int o,
                 int m,
                 boolean mb,
                 java.lang.String t,
                 GCounter gc)
        Constructor called for Railroad properties. Calls superclass constructor for any non unique property characteristics
        Parameters:
        n - String name of the Property
        p - int position of the Property
        c - int cost to purchase of the Property
        o - int current owner of the Property
        m - int value to mortgage the Property
        mb - boolean stating the mortgaged status of the Property
        t - String type of Property
        gc - GCounter object storing how many RProperties are owned
